<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13337</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17416</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布在烈日下走来走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17417</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他没有听到阿拉丁求助的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27772</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在想着那个灯和一个宏伟的计划。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27773</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很快我会比任何一个国王都富有！”他露出了邪恶的笑容。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会成为这个地球上最有权力的人！”马格里布一边笑一边跳舞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51123</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54970</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后他停下来皱了皱眉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54971</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61229</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个孩子在哪里？他去了很长时间了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61230</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65809</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然马格里布摸了摸他的耳朵。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65810</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68249</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他听到什么声音了吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68250</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“伯父！我回来了！你能听到我吗？”阿拉丁又叫了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80243</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布跑到入口处，从边缘往里看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80244</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85276</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你在做什么，孩子？快上来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85277</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89712</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“伯父，我上不来，”阿拉丁回答，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89713</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我拿了太重的东西，我爬不上最后一个台阶。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的口袋都满了，我的外套凸出来了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100723</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108047</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我从花园里拿了很多玻璃水果。请帮助我上去！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108048</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113527</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就只给我那盏灯，孩子。”马格里布严厉地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113528</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117310</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是那盏灯让你感觉很重。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117311</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123038</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给我那盏灯，然后你身上就会轻很多了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123039</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127793</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那盏灯？啊，对，那盏灯。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127794</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我放在身上某个地方了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136149</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，伯父，不是灯让我觉得很重。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136150</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那盏灯不重。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146030</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那盏灯在哪里？”马格里布很急切地问，“你对它做了什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146031</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153300</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我把它用我的腰带包起来，放在我后面的口袋里了。”阿拉丁说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153301</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157965</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很愿意上来之后给你。快帮我一下！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157966</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164865</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给我那盏灯，孩子！”魔法师生气地大声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164866</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173015</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我现在拿不到灯，”阿拉丁说，“你看？”他把手臂伸到背后。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173016</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180823</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我身上有很多玻璃水果，是给我妈妈的。”他伸进一个口袋里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180824</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186929</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是一个亮晶晶的红色的水果。你可以拿走它！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186930</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192821</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要！”马格里布大声说，“我不想要任何珠宝！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192822</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198665</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我只想要那盏灯！现在快给我！现在！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198666</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207344</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会的，伯父，我保证。”阿拉丁坚定地说，“但是我还不能给你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207345</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布为了让阿拉丁看到自己生气的脸，俯下了身。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216494</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的脸颊红得可怕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216495</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221665</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不服从我？”魔法师生气地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221666</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225743</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不能服从你，”阿拉丁说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225744</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227601</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232915</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布转过头，大声说：“你不能服从？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232916</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237874</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>魔法师跺着脚，他的周围都是灰尘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237875</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240694</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他用拳头打自己的头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240695</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245408</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不服从我？”他大声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245409</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他从袖子里拿出银色的盒子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不服从我？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布拿出一把粉末，念了一些咒语。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262638</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你会后悔的，你这个没用的小孩儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262639</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268865</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你在做什么，伯父？”阿拉丁大声说，“快帮我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268866</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273698</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布把粉末扔进火红的灰烬里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273699</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277510</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火焰射向了高空中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277511</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，我的孩子，现在你永远也出不来了！”他大声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285038</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287160</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“伯父！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287161</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290343</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大地又一次晃动了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290344</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295629</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在那个石阶上，阿拉丁看到大理石门开始关闭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295630</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300831</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那扇通向魔法宝物的门回到了原地。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300832</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>岩石和灰尘开始往下掉，完全把门给盖住了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布向天空挥舞着拳头，愤怒地扭动着身体。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313529</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>321280</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！！！”他呻吟道，“一切都被毁了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>321281</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>328153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“伯父！”阿拉丁在黑暗中大声说，“伯父！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>328154</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>335986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没有人听得见。没有人回答他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>